    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The Man With The Purple Gun",
        "Description": "\u201cSo, I have a question?\u201d\r\r\u201cYes, Agent 47.\u201d\r\r\u201cI get that it\u2019s a very well-balanced and silent gun, but may I ask - why is it purple?\u201d\r\r\u201cThe guys from engineering said it\u2019s imperative to its design. Something about being less detectable in the neon lights of Chongqing. Is it going to be a problem, Agent 47?\u201d\r\r\u201cNot at all.\u201d\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as YupItsPurple.",
